                <item type="punct" lang="hi">।</item>
              </word>
            </words>
            <item type="gls" lang="en">Just as Sherawali Maa is worshipped in Indore with faith and devotion, Maa Kali is worshipped in Kolkata with that very same faith.</item>
          </phrase>
        </phrases>
      </paragraph>
    </paragraphs>
    <languages>
